# =============================================================================
# TLS Private Key Placeholder
# =============================================================================
#
# This file has been replaced with a placeholder for security.
# The original contained a committed TLS private key.
#
# To generate a new key for testing:
#   openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:2048 -keyout tls-key.pem \
#     -out tls-cert.pem -days 365 -nodes -subj '/CN=localhost'
#
# Or use the gen-cert.js script:
#   node scripts/gen-cert.js
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit real TLS private keys to version control.
# =============================================================================
